Package io.oasp.module.jpa.dataaccess.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GenericRevisionedDao<ID,ENTITY extends MutablePersistenceEntity<ID>>
    This is the interface for a GenericDao with the ability of revision-control.
    RevisionedDao<ENTITY extends MutablePersistenceEntity<Long>>
    This is a simplified variant of GenericRevisionedDao for the suggested and common case that you have a Long as primary key.
    RevisionedMasterDataDao<E extends MutablePersistenceEntity<Long>>
    This is the interface for a Dao responsible for a PersistenceEntity that represents master-data.
